retrofit

Interface Converter<T>


  • public interface Converter<T>
    Convert objects to and from their representation as HTTP bodies. Register a converter with Retrofit using Retrofit.Builder.addConverter(Type, Converter) or Retrofit.Builder#addConverterFactory(Factory).
